        "heading": "<h2>80 serum-infused micro-darts for targeted care</h2>",
        "text": "<p>These advanced patches feature 80 ultra-fine, self-dissolving micro-darts designed to target and help <em>improve the appearance of fine lines, under-eye puffiness, and dark circles.</em><br/><br/>While traditional patches lay flat on the skin, the micro-dart design allows the serum to be applied in a more targeted, close-to-skin manner for enhanced contact and absorption. <br/><br/>Precisely engineered, the patches help support smoother-looking, more refreshed skin with consistent cosmetic use — including on delicate under-eye areas.</p>",
        "button_label": "Shop Now",
        "button_url": "#",
        "wistia_url": "f4cj3x9e99"
      }
    },
