          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/patches-ingredients-1.webp",
            "heading": "Retinol (Vitamin A)",
            "text": "<p>Retinol supports faster cell turnover to reveal smoother, more refined skin. It helps fade hyperpigmentation, improve texture, and reduce fine lines, without the typical irritation.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_mtbDUB": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/patches-ingredients-2.webp",
            "heading": "Copper Peptides ",
            "text": "<p>A blend of peptides designed to help support skin that looks firmer and more resilient, contributing to a plumper, more youthful look.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_gRweip": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/patches-ingredients-3.webp",
            "heading": "Caffeine",
            "text": "<p>Known for its refreshing properties, caffeine helps energize the look of tired skin and reduce the appearance of under-eye dullness and puffiness for a more awake look.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_fFymec": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/patches-ingredients-4.webp",
            "heading": "Licorice",
            "text": "<p>A botanical ingredient traditionally used in skincare to help soothe the look of stressed skin and promote a more even, calm-looking complexion.</p>"
          }
        },
        "dialog_nf9V8q": {
          "type": "dialog",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "View Full Ingredient List",
            "text": "<p><strong>Micro-Infusion Targeted Patches Ingredients</strong></p><p>Sodium Hyaluronate, Caffeine, Copper Tripeptide-1, Niacinamide, Cyclodextrin, Water, Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil, Madecassoside, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Allantoin, Retinol, Glycyrrhiza Glabra (Licorice) Root Extract, Centella Asiatica Extract, Acetyl Hexapeptide-8, BHT.</p>"
